  m_text: "<align=center><size=150%><color=#FFFFFF><b>H\u01B0\u1EDBng D\u1EABn Ch\u01A1i
    </b></color></size>\r\n\r\n<size=90%>B\u1EA1n \u0111i tr\u1EC5 ngay l\u1EA7n
    \u0111\u1EA7u event d\xE0nh cho sinh vi\xEAn m\u1EDBi </size>\r\n<size=85%>Event
    cho m\u1ED7i ng\u01B0\u1EDDi tham gia gi\u1EDBi h\u1EA1n th\u1EDDi gian th\u1EED
    th\xE1ch nh\u01B0ng v\xEC \u0111i mu\u1ED9n. B\u1EA1n ch\u1EC9 c\xF3 <color=#FF0000><b>18
    PH\xDAT</b></color> \u0111\u1EC3 d\xE0nh l\u1EA5y k\u1EBFt qu\u1EA3 totots nh\u1EA5t.\r\n\r\nH\xE3y
    thu th\u1EADp \u0111\u1EE7 b\u1ED9 <b>HUY CH\u01AF\u01A0NG</b>:\r\n<color=#FFD700><b>[V\xC0NG]</b></color>
    - <color=#C0C0C0><b>[B\u1EA0C]</b></color> - <color=#CD7F32><b>[\u0110\u1ED2NG]</b></color>\r\n\r\nM\u1ED7i
    Mini Game s\u1EBD trao lo\u1EA1i huy ch\u01B0\u01A1ng kh\xE1c nhau.\r\n<color=#CCCCCC><i>\"H\xE3y
    t\xEDnh to\xE1n th\u1EDDi gian... v\xE0 \u0111\u1EA1t th\xE0nh t\xEDch cao nh\u1EA5t\"</i></color></size>\r\n "
